# Civic Analysis Framework (CAF) v10.0 Analysis Report

**Experiment**: caf_civic_character_pattern_analysis  
**Run ID**: 44f3aaeea3648b16018f13e2086d957bc0feb27892d6e155e2b55d48886ab5a7  
